title: The Real Housewives Of Atlanta S06E21 Mess Rehearsal WEB-DL x264
description: With one week left until opening night of Kandi's musical, "A Mother's Love," Porsha heads to the studio to record her own single. Momma Joyce also stops by rehearsals and ends up having an open conversation with Todd on the future of their relationship. A shocking loss hits Kenya causing her to put aside all of the drama and realize what's important in life.
